Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:20:02.53,Spica - Signs,,0,0,90,,Tokyo National Space School
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:06.60,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa Family Grave
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.29,0:24:48.29,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Tokyo National Space School\NSeagull Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:32.19,Spica - Title,,0,0,90,,Test Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.43,0:24:36.43,Spica - Title,,0,0,90,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.43,0:25:00.14,Spica - Title,,0,0,90,,Space School Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:54.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:56.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Year 1, Class 1, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:01.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,My dream is to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:06.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's because I've heard that the Earth is very\Npretty when you look at it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:11.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,So I want to become a rocket driver and go into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:15.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I want to take people to all sorts of different planets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,And when they're on my rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:23.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...my dad and Lion-san will get special free rides!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:25.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:46.16,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Damn it! This is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's going to be totally impossible to line\Nall these up in these last two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,How many days do you think it took\Nus to line these up in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Or so he says, Fuchuuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Really, who do you think lined them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Damn monk haircut boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.09,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I don't want any more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I've had more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm getting outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:09.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,We're just gonna fail no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm telling you, just hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Calm down a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:21.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Don't mess with me!\NHow can I be calm!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's been bothering me for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:30.33,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,...but what do you think that is up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's a surveillance camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,A surveillance camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What, you never noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:42.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If you focus your eyes on it,\Nyou can see the inner lens moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,See? It just moved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:49.31,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Which would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,We were being watched this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:53.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:59.65,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I see. We were all mistakenly letting\Nourselves focus on the dominoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:04.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,This was originally supposed to be a\Nclosed-environment adaptation test, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:10.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Right. The most important thing will be to finish out the seven days here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's not about how many dominoes we line up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:20.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What reason would they have for shutting up three\Nguys who don't know each other in a room like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's the thing that the school wants to see the most, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Say it so people can understand what you mean, Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,In other words, the thing you're lacking most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:33.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:38.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Why are you always saying things that make people uncomfortable!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Who's doing that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.23,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:46.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I thought of a wonderful way to finish lining\Nup the dominoes in the last two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What? Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:54.33,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,It really is tiring having a moron in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.42,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,They must be observing everyone's progress from somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.59,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Actually, I wonder how that other moron is doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Pull yourself together, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Come on, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.31,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,What's wrong!? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:33.91,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.96,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Who's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.50,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,It's you, Lion-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.51,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Why do you look so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.22,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.68,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:03.15,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Why is Yuigahama burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.16,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Mom!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,She's calmed down a little bit now that she's lying down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:23.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...but it looks like she's not going to stop shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:26.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I wonder what could have happened to Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:30.68,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Her mind is just in turmoil from the stress\Nof this unfamiliar environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.85,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I'm sure it's a temporary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That would be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,She's been saying some weird things, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.34,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,You can tell by looking, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.07,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,We don't have any time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If you have time to be worrying about others...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...you should line some up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:53.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Really... Kamogawa-san is such a nuisance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:57.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Panicking over a little thing like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,It's proof that her spirit is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:06.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You know, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:13.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,She said she wanted to be friends with\Nyou from the bottom of her heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:17.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,And you're more worried about {\i1}these{\i0} than someone like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:20.93,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Is that supposed to be one of the astronaut\Nqualifications you talk about so much!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.45,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Hey, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:36.28,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Why won't Mom come back home with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.93,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Mom, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.76,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,It's me, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.39,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I'm always right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.02,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,Hey, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.98,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.02,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:45.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey, what do you think you're doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:48.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I don't want any more of this... not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I really should have pressed this button sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:57.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,When Asumi is suffering so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:01.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm mad at myself for hesitating like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:07.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Passing the test while she's suffering like that...\NI wouldn't be happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm sure I'd regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:13.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Because that just means I failed as a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Don't make it sound so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:20.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You're just pushing your suffering onto\NKamogawa-san, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:24.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You just want to run away and hide your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You're worried about Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You're just a simple hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Oh, look. Resorting to violence again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If you think you can change what people think like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...you're quite mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's something that weak people do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:48.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:56.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I've always looked up at the sky, ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:03.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I always, always, wanted to be closer to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's all that my dream is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.33,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,It's the only dream I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:14.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm sorry for worrying you, Kei-chan, Ukita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:18.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But I don't want to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I want to try my best a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:25.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Ukita-san, Kei-chan, I want to try my best with both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I get it, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Why don't you cool that off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I hate your guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...but I'll apologize for hitting you, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:00.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The feeling's mutual. I never want to go through this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What a brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I know... We need to get this done, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.47,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,We don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:15.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Stilt we have no choice but to get\Nas much done as we can, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:21.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Even after lights out, the light in the\Nbathroom still comes on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:35.21,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,This is your wonderful idea!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:41.30,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,It's just pulling all-nighters lining up the\Ndominoes with no breaks, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Well, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:46.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Hey, the one who came up with this plan better not be sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Please be a little quieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Even without your yelling, everyone's on edge already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I know that! Dammit...
Comment: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:12.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I always thought these tasted chalky, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:40.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,They're convenient for situations like this, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:43.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,They make them just for that reason, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Asumi, it's your turn next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Come on, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.83,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.09,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,We're not getting any sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,...so we need to at least eat properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,How about your drink?\NIs orange juice okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:12.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You're really good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm honored by your compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:37.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Although it tastes the same no matter who makes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:41.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:47.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Let's get these things lined up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Well, of course we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:19.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,We've been in this airtight room for two\Ndays without washing ourselves, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,No time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:21.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I haven't shampooed either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I can't show myself like this to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:30.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Ah, I want to take a full shower and really wash my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:33.93,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,You can shower as much as\Nyou want the day after we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,However, I'm not sure whether you'll be crying or laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Right, right. I'm lining them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I just have to line them up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Gochisousama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.73,Spica - Notes,,0,0,90,,"Gochisousama" is a phrase said after meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Just one more day of this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.27,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Just one more day until the exam is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.60,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Just one more day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.46,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Just two rooms, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:53.76,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,So thirteen teams lasted until the final day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:56.30,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,That's more than we expected, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:59.81,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,But that project must have been impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The dominoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I wonder who thought that one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Ah, check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Some of the rooms got all of them lined up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:27.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,0350 and 2960 did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:44.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Now I can finally take a shower...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You know, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:18:00.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,She said she wanted to be friends with\Nyou from the bottom of her heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.08,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,There's no way she could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:10.50,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,No one can understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:17.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,So if you think of this "river of heaven" as a real river...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:17.63,Spica - Notes,,0,0,90,,The Japanese term for the Milky Way galaxy is "river of heaven"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:23.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...each individual little star can be\Nthought of as bits of sand or g...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:25.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Gravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:29.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...gravel in that whole. This is again part of...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:34.32,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,As long as can I remember, since I was a very small child,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.19,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I almost never set foot outside of that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:42.37,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,If I tried to leave the room, I would be severely scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.17,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,The tutors who always came at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:55.05,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,The three meals a day that always came at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.71,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,The meals I spent alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.05,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,That forever unchanging life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.68,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,In that unchanging room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:05.81,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:11.06,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,The stars I could see from that window\Nso high up were the only...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.02,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,The stars were the only...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.57,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,The only thing that changed a bit, day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.57,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:24.07,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I, too, was always looking up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.83,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,She doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.58,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,There's no way anyone could understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:58.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Mom, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Now, one day, I'll be able to go into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:06.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I'll make sure to show you how I can\Nbecome a rocket driver, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.93,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:29.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Suzunari-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:35.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Really? So you passed the exam! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You're not happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:42.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm happy. Very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,When I think about things... and my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:51.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I start to wonder if it's really okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What do you think, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:57.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,About my desire to go into space...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:59.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What do you really think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The answer to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...is right here, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:09.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,No matter what the people around you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:16.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...you have to believe in your own dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:22.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm sure many people will say many different things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:25.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,And there may be times when you feel discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,When that happens, the answer is always right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.66,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,It's nowhere else but there inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:43.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,My dad hasn't seen this yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:57.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Congratulations, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:17.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,So these are the successful applicants' papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:26.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,So they'll be the first class of this new\Nastronaut training course, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:31.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's right. They'll be your students\Nstarting next semester, Sano-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:34.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,There sure are a lot of different kids!\NI'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:38.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Though saying that, I'll still only be their lecturer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:41.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I probably won't get too deeply involved with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:46.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Is there someone you know in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:49.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What? No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:54.41,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.10,0:24:45.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Of course I have Kei-chan and Ukita-san with me at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.61,0:24:48.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,And Fuchuuya-kun passed as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.32,0:24:53.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But I'm feeling just a bit lonely in the\Nnooks and crannies of my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.98,0:24:54.07,Spica - Notes,,0,0,90,,Banners: Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.03,0:24:57.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Next time on Twin Spica: Space School Entrance Ceremony.